title: The Secrets of Sleep 1b vhs xvid
description:
i placed the first part of this episode on Demonoid a few weeks ago (approx 28 min long).
this part looks at \&#039;out of body\&#039; experiences and night mares\&#039;. it also now tracked by sumotracker.

this is the second half of the first episode, which as i found out later are approx. 50 minutes long.
this is a vhs rip of a tv show aired in approx. 2000. sorry i cut most of the credits when i recorded it,
hence i don\&#039;t have much more info on it. if anyone has more info, please share.

this part looks at \&#039;dream telepathy\&#039;.
